HEADWORD: Benzile
<hw>Ben"zile</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Benzoin</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A yellowish crystalline
